Phrase: Victoria heard a mysterious voice in the dungeons. The person, who called herself "Anna", was a bandit who had broken into the castle to steal.
After being imprisoned, Anna took a liking to the daughter of the castle's owner and was hired as her daughter's maid of honour. However, she broke her ban and was sent back to prison.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: So she asked for help from Miss Victoria.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Yes. But Anna was not trying to save herself. Everything she did was to save the life of her mistress -- the young lady of the castle.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Hey, we shouldn't stay here for too long. We'll never know when this place will be filled with monsters. Let's get rid of the nasty things quickly, before we look for this Anna maid.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Anna went to the castle's other tower. Maybe she could go up to the rooftop to get to the room.
I'd like you to wait a minute. I agree that we should proceed with the investigation, but let's all calm down a bit. Especially you, Victoria. You're sweating badly.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Yes, it's true. You're in terrible cold sweat. I still think the bleeding in your head is affecting you.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: No, it can't be. Vivienne has treated my injuries and I feel fine. I feel no pain or fatigue.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: There may have been bad things in this dungeon. You should get some rest before you go.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I'm fine, really. There is no need to rest.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Then Yoshino and Vivienne will check you. Invisible curses are really scary.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: You are exaggerating. All I did was just speaking to Anna and opened the prison.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: That's enough. We are not exaggerating or anything.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: You exchanged words with an unknown person. You did as you were told and unlocked the prison. Immediately afterwards there was Phantom Mist.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: We might have been caught in a trap. Yoshino is worried about that. I don't mean to assume that this Anna person is a monster, but you should heed the advice of your friends.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: I apologize. I didn't think it through.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino isn't that good at words.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: But I can hardly believe that Anna was trying to harm me.
If Victoria says so, then it must be true. Victoria is the only one here who has heard Anna directly.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Sir Conductor...
But it is too early to take Anna's word for everything. There is still too little information to determine what is right.
It is fine to discuss. But I ask both Vivienne and Victoria to be a little more calm. I respect the opinion of all Train Knights. At least none of us are lying. Isn't that right?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oui, I agree. No one is lying.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Je suis désolé, Victoria. I didn't mean to sound like I was blaming you. I was just worried about your body...

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I know. I was the one who was preoccupied with Anna. She reminds me too much of myself.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: I can see that Victoria and Anna have become very close in the short time you've been together.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: I'm sure Anna felt the same way about you too, Victoria. That's why she approached you first.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Lady Paddington...
I would like to confirm one thing about this Anna, the maid... Has anyone seen her in person?

Name: Paddington
Phrase: None of us!

Name: Victoria
Phrase: By the time the lights came on, she was already gone.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: We didn't pass anyone either. We didn't feel any signs of people or footsteps.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: So this pattern is something that Yakky-tan is scared of.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: But it is true that Anna was locked up in this prison. And what she said is probably also true...

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Anna said, 'My mistress is being hunted by demons'. For some reason Anna's mistress perhaps put a curse on this castle to make it rain.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Even though she faints as soon as it rains?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Resistance to the parents who separated them, perhaps?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oh, I see. I hadn't thought of that. You're a great lady of a famous family after all.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: So there was a time when Queensway-kun was like that.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Please tell me one thing, Miss Yoshino. Is it impossible to lift a curse if something happens to the caster?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Not so many are like that, but those do exist. Curses that still linger after the caster dies are very difficult to break.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Did Anna say anything about curses?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: She said 'That this country will sink if we don't rescue her before she is kidnapped by demons'.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: This is a valley, yes. If the rain doesn't stop, this place will become a huge lake.

Name: Putra
Phrase: That sounds really bad, it won't be long before this dungeon sinks to the bottom of the water, you know?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: What's wrong, Putra?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Because the water in the drains is rising at an alarming rate.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: -Oh gosh, it's already above the floor!
One crisis after another. The drains around the dungeons have started to overflow. It seems that the heavy rain has finally started to flood the dungeons.

Name: Putra
Phrase: The way the water level is rising is not normal. This is not just a rain.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Then what's the cause?

Name: Putra
Phrase: I don't know, but we should get away from here. Look. Water is pouring in from all over the room.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Let's hurry up and get up there. If the lights go out again in this situation, we'll be in trouble.

Name: Putra
Phrase: This sound is, no way...?'

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino has a feeling it's a child who only bothers us when we're busy.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: The lights are on in this dark prison. Be careful not to get wet.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: There you are, Samantha. I am so relieved to see you even in Iris Metro.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Samantha, the Ghosts of the Mist. I see they are also present in Iris Cloud.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yes, some are useful, others kill people. There's not much good that comes out of meeting them. I hope that's not the case on your side of the world, but what are they really like?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Regrettably the Samanthas here are just as aware as Samanthas over there.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: The prison maid and the princess of the tower. The secret key is unobtainable.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: Yet the chambermaid is oblivious. She is so upset that she forgets the promise she made to the princess.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: 'It's a secret between them. It's one secret for both of them.'

Name: Samantha
Phrase: And yet they are not rewarded. There are too many enemies in the castle. They cannot escape alone.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: What are you talking about?

Name: Samantha
Phrase: Which key do you want? The key to the tower, the one the princess dropped? The key to the dungeon, which the chambermaid dropped? I'll lend you whichever you want.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: That's obvious. We are going to the tower, so we want the tower k...".

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Wait a minute. This is a Samantha's riddle. You can't just tell it what you want.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: I am asking the half-elf. The human, the elf and the shana, keep your mouths shut and wait.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: (I can't use my voice!)

Name: Versailles
Phrase: (Samantha did this.)

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Miss Queensway, Miss Versailles?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: You don't mean to tell me that everyone but me has been deprived of a voice...!
Apparently so. We all signal with our hands that we can't speak, with our mouths flapping. We have all been silenced by Samantha's magic.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: You give the answer and their voices return. Now choose which one you want. You alone decide.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: Which do you want? The key to the tower, which the princess dropped? The key to the dungeon, which the chambermaid dropped?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: I want... the dungeon key.

Name: Samantha
Phrase: Kekekekeke... What will happen, what will happen?
The moment Victoria chose the dungeon key, something fell with a clunk under Victoria's feet.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: It's a bunch of keys. It's numbered. It's the key to this dungeon.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Has your voice returned, ladies and gentlemen?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It's back. There's nothing unusual.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Victoria, why did you choose the dungeon key? The lock to the cell is open. You can't do anything with the key now.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: No, that's not true. The lock of the prison is not open. Anna's prison was only broken by me.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: That is true, but...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Girls! Talk later! The water level is rising again. We have to go now, it's really dangerous.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ditto. Yoshino's kept quiet until now, but... Yoshino's tail is already soaking wet.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Let's get out of this dungeon. We need to get up the stairs and get to safety!

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Please wait. Let me use this key to open all the prison doors before we escape.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Why? There's no one in the dungeon, remember?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: There was no one in the prison where Anna was. But Anna called for help from inside that prison. There may be others locked in other prisons who are not seen...

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Please, Sir Conductor. I beg you. All we have to do is to open all the locks. If we split and start opening it from the back, we should be able to escape in time. Please allow it.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: I beg you too.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: My Lady...

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Victoria doesn't say what she wants very often. But when she has a strong hunch, she can suddenly be very selfish. That intuition has saved my life on many occasions.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: When my mother's men were ambushing her; when my father's men were ambushing her, and even my sister Islington's men were ambushing her. Victoria has used her natural instincts to evade all enemy's attacks.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The fact that all of Paddington's enemies are family.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: I'm sure the Samantha dropped those keys for a reason. Otherwise we'd all be Samantha by now!

Name: Victoria
Phrase: That's not true, Milady.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Anyway, let's all split up and unlock the prison. The shorter ones, please start from the prison near the doorway. Yoshino, Yakutsk, Versailles!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You too, I presume!

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Hawawa! That's right! So, Sir Conductor, you take care of that one!
Since Paddington said yes, I'll trust Victoria's instincts here. If something goes wrong because of these locks, then so be it.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Thank you. If anything goes wrong, I will take responsibility for it.
No, no. If anything goes wrong, we all will. If you protect me there, I'll allow you to unlock the dungeon.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Yes!
